Step 1: Install the required libraries
      pip install opencv-python face_recognition numpy pandas

Step 2: Prepare your dataset
        You need a dataset of images of students with their names as labels. Organize your images in a folder structure like this:
            dataset/
            student_name1/
            image1.jpg
            image2.jpg
            student_name2/
            image1.jpg
            image2.jpg
            
